repTourPittsburgh

blog.description:
26 years young. Pittsburgh, PA. Psychiatric RN. Married to my high school sweetheart. Dog mom. Taylor Swift has been my favorite since 2006. repTourColumbus Flr E, Row 2, Seat 29&30. repTourPittsburgh Center Pit!

taylornation reblogged our photo at repTourColumbus!

summary: We’re K and B the Kat Burglars of repTourPittsburgh! Be on the lookout for us in center pit! We “did something bad..” We are...
caption:
We’re K and B the Kat Burglars of repTourPittsburgh! Be on the lookout for us in center pit! We “did something bad..” We are wanted for “Stealing hearts and running off and never saying sorry;” we also “put the money in a bag and stole the keys” and took off in our “Getaway Car.” Last seen at repTourColumbus posing as the tAy-team in red reputation jerseys armed with Olivia and Meredith cat puppets.

Our names are Kaleigh and Bryanna. We are both 26. We have been best friends since elementary school. We really do call each other K and B. We grew up together. We have been through it all together- from awkward middle school years to first heartbreaks to K having her beautiful babygirl to K even being the maid of honor at B’s wedding. We love to have fun together and laugh at ourselves hence our Getaway Car videos and photos. We also did another photoshoot having a memorial since the old Taylor is dead; we also celebrated the new Taylor! (Shoutout to B’s husband and K’s boyfriend who are also best friends and put up with our Taylor shenanigans by helping us to set up and be part of the photos and also be our photographers) We have so much in common, especially our love for Taylor Swift. We not only grew up together, but we also grew with Taylor. Her songs helped us get through life’s best and worst times over the past twelve years. We know we will always have each other. So “here’s a toast to our real friends”… and to @taylorswift We love you and appreciate everything you do for your fans! @taylornation

question: hiiii! if you’re ever thinking about using songs for inspiration or do a fic based on one i think you should take a look at The Other Side - Jason Derulo and Ours - Taylor Swift idk, but i feel like those would make good fics
answer:
Hi! Woah, I haven’t listened to either of those songs in years - but I absolutely love them! And I agree! They would make great fic prompts! I love writing with a song prompt and I would love to do some after I finish my requests! Ily! ❤ xx

(Now I’m just listening to them on repeat tbh, trying to think up storylines - The Other Side, Ours)
